e coupled DM\ncomponent, in spite of its small density parameter, after the warm component\nhas become non-relativistic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jun 2012 16:41:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Aug 2012 10:51:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-15"}
