 superlattice geometry thus provides new opportunities for controlled\nmodification of the electron-phonon interaction in complex materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jun 2012 19:37:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-28"}
