ic phase. If the Ekpyrotic phase is preceded by a period of\nmatter-dominated contraction, the primordial power spectrum is nearly\nscale-invariant on large scales (scales which exit the Hubble radius in the\nmatter-dominated phase) but acquires a large blue tilt on small scales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jun 2012 21:12:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Jun 2012 16:59:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-21"}
